title: Iguanodon Discog (4 Albums)
description:
I really didn't want to do this, but someone has to, for great justice. Iguanodon keeps posting his non-Fright Sprites albums for purchase and either he, or someone else keeps taking them down. So here they are. If you dig it, get over to his bandcamp and email him and tell him to get sober enough to keep his awesome tunes online.

I LOVE YOU IGUANODON PEACE LOVE IGUANODON
